B.I1=new A.bq(B.tB,["CAMOUFLAGE","AI L\xc0 K\u1eba NGO\u1ea0I \u0110\u1ea0O?","CH\u01a0I NGAY!","LU\u1eacT CH\u01a0I","LU\u1eacT CH\u01a0I D\u1ec4 \u1eb8C","Tr\xf2 ch\u01a1i chia l\xe0m 3 phe: D\xe2n th\u01b0\u1eddng, N\u1ed9i gi\xe1n v\xe0 Mr. White.\n\n\u2022 D\xe2n th\u01b0\u1eddng \ud83e\udd20: Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\xf9ng m\u1ed9t t\u1eeb kh\xf3a. Nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5: T\xecm ra k\u1ebb kh\xe1c bi\u1ec7t.\n\n\u2022 N\u1ed9i gi\xe1n \ud83e\udd77: Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1eeb kh\xf3a na n\xe1 d\xe2n th\u01b0\u1eddng. Nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5: Tr\xe0 tr\u1ed9n v\xe0 s\u1ed1ng s\xf3t.\n\n\u2022 Mr. White \ud83d\udc7b: KH\xd4NG c\xf3 t\u1eeb kh\xf3a. Nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5: \u1ea8n m\xecnh v\xe0 h\xf3ng h\u1edbt xem t\u1eeb c\u1ee7a d\xe2n th\u01b0\u1eddng l\xe0 g\xec.\n\nC\xe1ch ch\u01a1i: M\u1ed7i v\xf2ng, t\u1eebng ng\u01b0\u1eddi n\xe9m ra 1 t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ec3 mi\xeau t\u1ea3 t\u1eeb kh\xf3a c\u1ee7a m\xecnh (Kh\xf4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c khai to\u1eb9t ra nh\xe9). Sau \u0111\xf3 c\u1ea3 \u0111\xe1m nh\u1ea3y v\xe0o m\u1ed5 x\u1ebb v\xe0 vote lo\u1ea1i 1 \u0111\u1ee9a kh\u1ea3 nghi nh\u1ea5t!","OK, \u0110\xc3 HI\u1ec2U!","THI\u1ebeT L\u1eacP","D\xe2n Th\u01b0\u1eddng","C\xf9ng chung ch\xed h\u01b0\u1edbng","N\u1ed9i Gi\xe1n","H\u01a1i l\u1ea1c qu\u1ebb m\u1ed9t ch\xfat","Mr. White","K\u1ebb m\xf9 m\u1edd","T\u1ed4NG C\u1ed8NG: ","TI\u1ebeP T\u1ee4C","G\xec v\u1eady? Ph\u1ea3i c\xf3 \xedt nh\u1ea5t 3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi ch\u1ee9!","\u0110I\u1ec2M DANH","Ng\u01b0\u1eddi ch\u01a1i","V\xc0O VI\u1ec6C TH\xd4I!","\u0110\u01b0a m\xe1y cho","CH\u1ea0M \u0110\u1ec2 XEM T\u1eea C\u1ee6A B\u1ea0N","T\u1eea KH\xd3A C\u1ee6A B\u1ea0N L\xc0:","Su\u1ef5t! Gi\u1eef b\xed m\u1eadt nh\xe9!","B\u1ea1n KH\xd4NG c\xf3 t\u1eeb kh\xf3a (Mr. White)","OK, \u0110\xc3 NH\u1eda!","Tuy\u1ec7t \u0111\u1ed1i kh\xf4ng cho ai xem m\xe0n h\xecnh n\xe0y!","\u0110\u1ebeN L\u01af\u1ee2T C\u1ee6A:","N\xe9m ra 1 t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ec3 mi\xeau t\u1ea3 t\u1eeb kh\xf3a c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n \u0111i!","XONG, \u0110\u1ebeN NG\u01af\u1edcI TI\u1ebeP THEO","B\xd3C PH\u1ed0T & VOTE","Ai l\xe0 k\u1ebb kh\u1ea3 nghi nh\u1ea5t? B\u1ea7u m\u1ed9t ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec3 ti\u1ec5n l\xean b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ebfm s\u1ed1!","CH\u1eccN 1 NG\u01af\u1edcI \u0110\u1ec2 LO\u1ea0I:","LO\u1ea0I","CH\u1ed0T \u0110\u01a0N","B\u1ea1n ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn mu\u1ed1n ti\u1ec5n","QUAY L\u1ea0I","\u0110\xc3 B\u1eca LO\u1ea0I!","Th\xe2n ph\u1eadn th\u1eadt s\u1ef1 l\xe0","D\xc2N TH\u01af\u1edcNG TH\u1eaeNG!","K\u1eba NGO\u1ea0I \u0110\u1ea0O TH\u1eaeNG!","MR. WHITE TH\u1eaeNG!","N\u1ed8I GI\xc1N TH\u1eaeNG!","T\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 K\u1ebb Ngo\u1ea1i \u0110\u1ea1o \u0111\xe3 b\u1ecb qu\xe9t s\u1ea1ch kh\u1ecfi b\u1ea3n \u0111\u1ed3.","D\xe2n th\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\xe3 b\u1ecb l\u1eeba g\u1ea1t to\xe0n t\u1eadp.","Mr. White \u0111\xe3 \u0111o\xe1n \u0111\xfang t\u1eeb kh\xf3a ho\u1eb7c s\u1ed1ng s\xf3t \u0111\u1ebfn cu\u1ed1i.","N\u1ed9i gi\xe1n \u0111\xe3 ti\xeau di\u1ec7t h\u1ebft d\xe2n th\u01b0\u1eddng.","C\u01a0 H\u1ed8I CU\u1ed0I CHO MR. WHITE","Mr. White, b\u1ea1n \u0111\xe3 b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i! H\xe3y g\xf5 t\u1eeb kh\xf3a c\u1ee7a D\xe2n th\u01b0\u1eddng m\xe0 b\u1ea1n \u0111o\xe1n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\xe0o \u0111\xe2y \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1eadt ng\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ebf c\u1edd:","Nh\u1eadp t\u1eeb kh\xf3a...","KI\u1ec2M TRA","T\u1eeb c\u1ee7a D\xe2n th\u01b0\u1eddng: ","T\u1eeb c\u1ee7a N\u1ed9i gi\xe1n: ","CH\u01a0I V\xc1N N\u1eeeA"],t.li)
B.I0=new A.bq(B.tB,["CAMOUFLAGE","WHO IS THE IMPOSTOR?","PLAY NOW!","HOW TO PLAY","EASY RULES","The game has 3 roles: Civilians, Undercover, and Mr. White.\n\n\u2022 Civilians \ud83e\udd20: Everyone gets the same secret word. Goal: Find the odd one out.\n\n\u2022 Undercover \ud83e\udd77: Gets a word slightly different. Goal: Blend in and survive.\n\n\u2022 Mr. White \ud83d\udc7b: Gets NO word. Goal: Hide and guess the civilians' word.\n\nHow to play: Each round, everyone gives 1 word to describe their secret word. Then discuss and vote out the most suspicious person!","GOT IT!","SETUP","Civilian","Shares the same word","Undercover","Has a slightly different word","Mr. White","Has no word","TOTAL PLAYERS: ","NEXT","Come on, we need at least 3 players!","ROLL CALL","Player","LET'S GO!","Pass the device to","TAP TO VIEW YOUR WORD","YOUR WORD IS:","Shh! Keep it a secret!","You have NO word (Mr. White)","OK, I GOT IT!","Do not show this screen to anyone!","SPEAKING TURN:","Drop 1 clue word to describe your secret word!","DONE, NEXT PERSON","DISCUSS & VOTE","Who is the impostor? Vote someone out!","CHOOSE SOMEONE TO ELIMINATE:","VOTE OUT","CONFIRM","Are you sure you want to eliminate","CANCEL","WAS ELIMINATED!","Their real role was","CIVILIANS WIN!","IMPOSTORS WIN!","MR. WHITE WINS!","UNDERCOVER WINS!","All impostors have been wiped out.","Civilians were completely fooled.","Mr. White guessed the word correctly or survived.","Undercovers have eliminated all civilians.","LAST CHANCE FOR MR. WHITE","Mr. White, you are eliminated! Type the Civilian's word you guess to steal the win:","Type the word...","CHECK GUESS","Civilian word: ","Undercover word: ","PLAY AGAIN"],t.li)
